data.description: Find the house of your dreams in this master-planned neighborhood. This large 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home has a traditional kitchen, an upgraded fireplace, and an opulent master suite. Enjoy the community pool, as well as the stores and schools that are close by. It never flooded in this house. The perfect balance of comfort, style, and convenience can be found in this house. Seize the opportunity to claim it as your own!
